166	1	2013-06-24 12:54:18	2013-06-24 04:54:18	<p>The ninth installment of the National Youth Congress was held on August 31, 2012 at the P&G Room of the UP College of Business Administration and on September 1, 2012 at the GT-Toyota Asian Center Auditorium. Titled <em>Pedaling Towards Prosperity: The Pursuit for Progressive Development</em>, it focused on Philippine economic development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NYC 2012 was notable for being the first to have participating high schools from Luzon, Visayas, and Mindanao. It was also the first not to be held at the UP School of Economics Auditorium, which was being renovated at the time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    Click on the links below to learn more about NYC 2012:<ul>\r\n        <li><a href="poster">Poster</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href="schools">Schools</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href="speakers">Speakers</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href="organizer">Organizer</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href="pictures">Pictures</a></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</p>	NYC 2012		inherit	open	open		40-revision-25			2013-06-24 12:54:18	2013-06-24 04:54:18		40	http://localhost/wordpress/40-revision-25/	0	revision		0
