\n\r\n<p>It was officially endorsed by the <a href="http://neda.gov.ph/about.asp" target="_blank">National Economic and Development Authority</a> for the first time in 2008 and by the <a href="http://deped.gov.ph/" target="_blank">Department of Education</a> in 2009. In 2010, the Congress expanded into a two-day event, with some delegates receiving accommodations at the University Hotel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Last year, the NYC tackled the burgeoning field of Behavioral Economics, inviting speakers from both the economics and psychology disciplines. It was also preceded by <a href="http://fb.com/inkling.ph" target="_blank">Inkling</a>, a writing seminar/competition that featured an exclusive <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sUfDTywtQ3c" target="_blank">message</a> from reclusive author <a href="http://www.visprint.net/publications/bob/index.htm" target="_blank">Bob Ong</a>.</p>	About		inherit	open	open		4-revision-8			2013-06-17 13:42:27	2013-06-17 05:42:27		4	http://localhost/wordpress/4-revision-8/	0	revision		0
